//
// ProcessContainerPlus.js
// Copyright (C) 2026 Brannon Quel
//
// One-click preprocessing pipeline for linear astronomical images.
// Inputs: 1-5 cropped, star-aligned, plate-solved linear grayscale or color images.
//
// Pipeline:
//   1. BlurXTerminator (correct only — linear PSF fix)
//   2. GradientCorrection (automatic convergence)
//   3. SPCC (ideal QE curve, avg spiral galaxy, requires WCS)
//   4. BlurXTerminator (full sharpen pass)
//   5. MultiscaleAdaptiveStretch
//   6. StarXTerminator (unscreen, large overlap option)
//   7. NoiseXTerminator
//
// Version history:
//   1.0  2026  Initial release
//   1.1  2026  Added save star image checkbox to StarXTerminator step
//   1.2  2026  Renamed to ProcessContainerPlus
//   1.3  2026  Removed STF change, fixed star image detection via window snapshot
//   1.4  2026  Fixed star image (Stars=true), added BN step, DRC slider, fixed slider precision
//   1.5  2026  Fixed StarX lowercase property names, fixed all slider precision
//   1.6  2026  Fixed SPCC/NoiseX properties, fixed naming convention, added presets
//   1.7  2026  Fixed double StarX/NoiseX, Photon Flux for narrowband, halos slider, NoiseX options
//   1.8  2026  Auto-apply presets, default Manual, halos reordered, settings persistence, reset clears saved
//   4.3  2026  Star Removal redesign: dropdown (None/Linear/Stretched), new clone color sat slider,
//              removed Recombine option, fixed stray mgcRef ghost control, MGC-only visibility fixes
//   4.4  2026  Filter auto-detect OIII/SII fix, MARS paths visibility fix (Control wrapper),
//              Console.show() after GraXpert, NoiseX UI redesign (4-channel dynamic sliders, drop detail),
//              pipeline summary in preset box, step timing in console output
//   4.5  2026  UI compaction (BN/SPCC row, StarX/overlap row, grad model inline, SPCC refs row,
//              output row, NoiseX master+checkboxes row), MGC note updated, pipeline summary
//              font/color improved, end-of-pipeline step timing summary block in console
//   1.0  2026  Public release: tooltip cleanup (removed external script references), Help button added
//   1.1  2026  Pipeline summary label black, NoiseX linked sliders checkbox

